    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">This complete tennis playset comes with 2 rackets and 2 matching tennis balls, making it a great outdoor play option for kids. The rackets and balls are both constructed of durable plastic that will ensure hours and hours of fun, rain or shine. They come in bright neon colors, and the handles feature foam grips for comfort during playtime.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">TychoTyke Kids Tennis Racket Play Set Rackets Balls Outdoor Exercise (2 Colors)</h2>\n  <p>Add some fun exercise to playtime with the TychoTyke Kids Tennis Racket Play Set!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>PROMOTES EXERCISE - Tennis Is a Great Way for Kids to Get Outdoor Exercise During Playtime</li>\n    <li>TEACHES HAND-EYE COORDINATION - Kids Will Learn How to Quickly React and Improve Balance</li>\n    <li>COMPLETE SET - Comes with 2 Rackets and 2 Matching Balls for 2 Person Tennis Matches</li>\n    <li>DURABLE CONSTRUCTION - Made of Sturdy Plastic That Will Ensure Hours of Fun, Rain or Shine</li>\n    <li>AGES 3 AND UP - Designed for Children At Least 3 Years of Age | Great Gift Idea for Young Kids</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/toys/XY9908_racket_set_var.jpg\" alt=\"Add some fun exercise to playtime with the TychoTyke Kids Tennis Racket Play Set\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> TTTRACK</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 060886753025/060886231530</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This complete tennis playset comes with 2 rackets and 2 matching tennis balls, making it a great outdoor play option for kids. The rackets and balls are both constructed of durable plastic that will ensure hours and hours of fun, rain or shine. They come in bright neon colors, and the handles feature foam grips for comfort during playtime.</p>\n  <p>Tennis is a great way for kids to get some outdoor exercise, and they can learn about the importance of hand-eye coordination. This set is designed for children ages 3 and up. Make sure to grab a set of these for your little ones!</p>\n  <p>2 Color Options Available: Blue/Yellow or Pink/Yellow</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
